<p>Dr. Smith,</p>
<p>Congratulations on receiving your doctorate. I'm&#8230; skeptical regarding the applications of such a thesis, especially how it pertains to Site-90.</p>
<p>Are you feeling alright? It's normal for graduate studies to take a toll on your well-being, but last I saw you, you were unusually&#8230; stiff, is the only word that comes to mind. Take a breather: you're done. Worry about some self-replicating pizza toppings for the time being.<br /></p>
