<p>Hello, and sorry for the third email in a month.</p>
<p>Is there any progress on the Chamber 02 case? It doesn't feel like too much it's been fixed; actually, it feels like it's gotten worse. The smell's starting to spread outside the chamber proper, and the construction noises aren't any quieter. Whatever they're doing when they're not expanding, it's still happening.</p>
